<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="proxy-page" data-turbo="false">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Vialink</title>
  <style>
    /* Modern CTA Overlay Styles - 2025 Design */
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html.proxy-page, body.proxy-page {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    }

    .proxy-page #content-frame {
      width: 100%;
      height: calc(100% - 100px);
      border: none;
      display: block;
    }

    .proxy-page #cta-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: auto;
      min-height: 100px;
      padding: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.98) 100%);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 -4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      z-index: 9999;
      border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .cta-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .cta-text {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1f2937;
      flex: 0 1 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
    }

    .cta-button:active {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    #iframe-error {
      display: none;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #fef2f2;
      border: 2px solid #fecaca;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin: 40px;
    }

    #iframe-error h2 {
      color: #991b1b;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    #iframe-error a {
      color: #667eea;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .proxy-page #content-frame {
        height: calc(100% - 140px);
      }

      .cta-content {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .cta-text {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .cta-button {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 14px 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="proxy-page">
  <iframe id="content-frame" src="<%= @link.original_url %>"></iframe>

  <div id="iframe-error">
    <h2>⚠️ 이 콘텐츠는 프레임에서 표시할 수 없습니다</h2>
    <p>대상 웹사이트의 보안 설정으로 인해 여기에 표시할 수 없습니다.</p>
    <p><a href="<%= @link.original_url %>" target="_blank">여기를 클릭하여 원본 페이지를 방문하세요</a></p>
  </div>

  <div id="cta-overlay">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <% if @link.cta_text.present? %>
        <span class="cta-text"><%= @link.cta_text %></span>
      <% end %>
      <% if @link.cta_link.present? %>
        <a href="<%= @link.cta_link %>" class="cta-button" target="_blank">
          <%= @link.cta_button_text || '자세히 보기' %>
        </a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Detect if iframe fails to load (X-Frame-Options blocking)
    const iframe = document.getElementById('content-frame');
    const errorDiv = document.getElementById('iframe-error');

    iframe.addEventListener('error', function() {
      iframe.style.display = 'none';
      errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
    });

    // Timeout fallback (some browsers don't fire error event)
    setTimeout(function() {
      try {
        const iframeDoc = iframe.contentDocument || iframe.contentWindow.document;
        if (!iframeDoc) {
          iframe.style.display = 'none';
          errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
        }
      } catch (e) {
        // Cross-origin access denied - this is actually normal
        // Only show error if iframe is completely empty
      }
    }, 3000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
